            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>sesame lean pork & egg fried rice</strong> in bowls</p><p>Garnish with the <strong>chopped spring onion</strong> and<strong> sesame seeds</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
      "order": 8,
